high_descs: Turn to the left to face the sink on the right.
Pick the toilet paper roll up from the floor to the left of the toilet.
Move over to the right side of the toilet.
Put the roll on the back of the toilet.
Cross the room to face the gray trash can.
Pick the toilet paper roll up from the trash can.
Turn around and cross the room to stand on the right side of the toilet.
Put the toilet paper roll on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put an empty and one full toilet paper roll on the back of a toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and step forward to face the right end of the sink.
Pick up the empty roll on the sink.
Take a step to the right to face the back of the toilet.
Place the empty roll on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the trash can on the floor.
Pick up the toilet paper in the trash can.
Turn around and walk forward to face the toilet.
Place the toilet paper on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: To move a toilet paper roll plus an empty roll to the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper roll on the floor.
Turn around and head to the right side of the toilet.
Put the toilet paper roll on the back of the toilet
Turn left, go across the room, turn right and go to the trash can.
Pick up the toilet paper roll in the trash can.
Turn around and go back to the toilet.
Put the toilet paper on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two toilet paper rolls on the back of the toilet.
